1
00:01:48,833 --> 00:01:50,416
Shit!

2
00:01:57,625 --> 00:02:02,250
Someone from down that road
is going to come for me.

3
00:02:05,583 --> 00:02:08,041
Sorry about the wait, Hana.

4
00:02:10,583 --> 00:02:12,541
I came to get you.

5
00:02:46,958 --> 00:02:48,541
I got a call this morning.

6
00:02:48,625 --> 00:02:51,541
They said one of
the children was missing.

7
00:02:51,625 --> 00:02:53,708
Joaquim Sanchez.

8
00:02:53,791 --> 00:02:57,625
Apparently he stole
some of my money and ran away.

9
00:02:57,708 --> 00:03:00,416
You know we can't
bring the police into this.

10
00:03:00,500 --> 00:03:02,291
If word gets out
we've been selling children,

11
00:03:02,375 --> 00:03:04,041
we'll all be finished.

12
00:03:04,125 --> 00:03:06,583
Now get out there
and find this brat!

13
00:03:09,000 --> 00:03:10,875
Don't you have some
work you should be doing?

14
00:03:10,958 --> 00:03:12,791
It's fine.

15
00:03:15,083 --> 00:03:16,458
And there they go.

16
00:03:16,541 --> 00:03:17,958
Which one are you betting on?

17
00:03:18,041 --> 00:03:19,041
Marco?

18
00:03:19,125 --> 00:03:22,000
Or the bull?

19
00:03:22,083 --> 00:03:24,250
Buzz the hell off, jerk.

20
00:03:28,416 --> 00:03:29,458
Welcome--

21
00:03:30,458 --> 00:03:31,916
You hag!

22
00:03:39,541 --> 00:03:43,250
You wanna tell me why the hell
you sent Hatchin away like that?

23
00:03:44,875 --> 00:03:47,875
You don't even have the common
courtesy to give me a "hello,"

24
00:03:47,958 --> 00:03:50,625
yet you ask me
to take in a child?

25
00:03:50,708 --> 00:03:52,875
And now you think coming
in here shouting insults

26
00:03:52,958 --> 00:03:55,041
is what a parent deserves?

27
00:03:55,125 --> 00:03:56,916
Ain't no fuckin' parent here!

28
00:03:59,583 --> 00:04:01,666
You don't fool me, Michiko.

29
00:04:01,750 --> 00:04:04,625
You may have a big grown-up
body now to turn men's heads,

30
00:04:04,708 --> 00:04:06,541
but in my eyes
you're still that immature,

31
00:04:06,625 --> 00:04:08,208
snot-nosed little girl.

32
00:04:08,291 --> 00:04:09,875
Listen'a me.

33
00:04:09,958 --> 00:04:11,958
Thanks to your stupid ass,
Hatchin's been taken

34
00:04:12,041 --> 00:04:13,458
by Fantasma.

35
00:04:13,541 --> 00:04:15,333
That's got nothin'
to do with me.

36
00:04:15,416 --> 00:04:17,666
Shirkov the Third
suddenly charges in!

37
00:04:17,750 --> 00:04:19,791
He's sending Marco
a strong message:

38
00:04:19,875 --> 00:04:22,500
"You may have landed some
blows, but I'm still the boss!

39
00:04:22,583 --> 00:04:24,625
Can Marco hold on?"

40
00:04:27,625 --> 00:04:30,083
Now Marco braces
for the attack!

41
00:04:33,541 --> 00:04:34,833
He's done it!

42
00:04:34,916 --> 00:04:38,875
Marco has masterfully
defeated Shirkov the Third!

43
00:04:38,958 --> 00:04:40,166
And who the hell is he?

44
00:04:40,250 --> 00:04:41,916
Your lover?

45
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,541
Or is--

46
00:04:46,166 --> 00:04:48,458
If anything's happened
to her, you're gonna pay, hag!

47
00:04:48,541 --> 00:04:51,083
Mark my damn words!

48
00:04:51,166 --> 00:04:52,875
Sure hon, whatever.

49
00:04:54,833 --> 00:04:56,791
Hold on.

50
00:04:56,875 --> 00:05:00,583
After all these years,
why'd you send her to me?

51
00:05:00,666 --> 00:05:02,583
'Cause in spite
of everything else,

52
00:05:02,666 --> 00:05:05,333
you taught me
to believe in you.

53
00:05:05,416 --> 00:05:08,583
You taught me to trust you!

54
00:05:08,666 --> 00:05:10,791
After all these years
I realized.

55
00:05:10,875 --> 00:05:13,875
Someone who thinks that way
can't have any deceit in them.

56
00:05:13,958 --> 00:05:14,833
Then again.

57
00:05:14,916 --> 00:05:16,625
You just tricked me.

58
00:05:16,708 --> 00:05:19,625
Shows ya what the
fuck I know, right?

59
00:05:19,708 --> 00:05:22,916
If she's hurt, I'll put you
on an express train to hell.

60
00:05:33,166 --> 00:05:34,458
Atsuko!

61
00:05:59,291 --> 00:06:01,458
You sold off Iolanda, right?

62
00:06:01,541 --> 00:06:03,291
Where did she go?

63
00:06:03,375 --> 00:06:04,833
She'll be happier.

64
00:06:04,916 --> 00:06:06,416
That's a flat-out lie.

65
00:06:06,500 --> 00:06:08,125
You sold her somewhere awful!

66
00:06:08,208 --> 00:06:09,375
That should be her money!

67
00:06:09,458 --> 00:06:11,666
So why shouldn't
I take it to her?

68
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:13,916
Tell me Michiko.

69
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,708
Why do you assume the worst
about me every single time?

70
00:06:16,791 --> 00:06:18,000
'Cause it's true!

71
00:06:18,083 --> 00:06:19,000
What's wrong?

72
00:06:19,083 --> 00:06:21,208
Can't you trust me
even a little?

73
00:06:24,041 --> 00:06:26,375
Greedy old hags like you
should go straight to hell,

74
00:06:26,458 --> 00:06:28,708
and I should send
you there myself!

75
00:06:28,791 --> 00:06:29,833
You're a hag!

76
00:06:29,916 --> 00:06:32,125
A dirty old hag!

77
00:06:39,458 --> 00:06:41,000
That's enough!

78
00:06:43,375 --> 00:06:44,916
Don't--!

79
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,708
C'mon.

80
00:06:45,791 --> 00:06:46,625
Let's go home.

81
00:06:46,708 --> 00:06:48,916
Lemme go, you old hag!

82
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,333
